```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #000;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 120px;
      color: #FFD700;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    p {
      color: #ccc;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      background: #FFD700;
      color: #000;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #fff;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Animation */
    .glow {
      animation: glow 1.5s infinite alternate;
    }

    @keyframes glow {
      from {
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #FFD700;
      }
      to {
        text-shadow: 0 0 25px #FFD700, 0 0 40px #FFD700;
      }
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="glow">404</h1>
    <h2>Oops! Page Not Found</h2>
    <p>The page you are looking for might have been removed or doesn't exist.</p>
    
    <a href="/" class="btn">Go Back Home</a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
```
